<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_English_Novel_From_Dickens_to_Lawrence&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="The English Novel From Dickens to Lawrence (page does not exist)">The English Novel From Dickens to Lawrence</a>,</i> London Chatto and Windus, 1970. Reprinted, London, Hogarth Press, 1985</li>
