<li>M. Axton and R. Williams (eds) <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=English_Drama:_Forms_and_Developments&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="English Drama: Forms and Developments (page does not exist)">English Drama: Forms and Developments</a>,</i> Essays in Honour of Muriel Clara Bradbrook, with an introduction by R. Williams, Cambridge and New York, Cambridge University Press, 1977.</li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Marxism_and_Literature_(book_by_Raymond_Williams)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Marxism and Literature (book by Raymond Williams) (page does not exist)">Marxism and Literature</a>,</i> Marxist Introductions Series, London and New York, Oxford University Press, 1977. Translated into Spanish, Italian and Korean.</li>
