<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Problems_in_Materialism_and_Culture:_Selected_Essays&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Problems in Materialism and Culture: Selected Essays (page does not exist)">Problems in Materialism and Culture: Selected Essays</a>,</i> London, Verso, 1980. New York, Schocken, 1981. Reissued as <i>Culture and Materialism</i>, Verso Radical Thinkers Series, 2005.</li>
