<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Cobbett_(book_by_Raymond_Williams)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Cobbett (book by Raymond Williams) (page does not exist)">Cobbett</a></i>, Past Masters series, Oxford and New York, Oxford University Press, 1983.</li>
