<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Writing_in_Society_(book_by_Raymond_Williams)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Writing in Society (book by Raymond Williams) (page does not exist)">Writing in Society</a> ,</i> London, Verso, 1983. US edition. New York, Verso, 1984</li>
